<plot>This documentary focuses on the life of Garfield creator Jim Davis leading up to the creation of his famous feline. Interviews and archival footage provide an interesting look into one of the most successful artists ever to have worked in the comic strip industry. This piece was created for the Garfield: The Movie DVD release.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?544134</url></doc>
